    "descriptionModule": {
      "briefSummary": "This trial is seeking to determine whether a single 4mg intranasal dose of bumetanide acutely reduces pulmonary artery pressure and blood volume in the outpatient setting for patients with heart failure and an implanted device for remote patient monitoring (i.e. Cordella or CardioMEMS)."
    },
